item.title: Discover the Secret to Turning Off SOS on Your iPhone 12 Mini!
item.description: Introduction Are you the proud owner of a new iPhone 12 Mini? If so, you may have noticed the Emergency SOS feature, which is designed to help you in an emergency situation. While this feature is great to have, it can be a bit of a nuisance if it is accidentally triggered. Fortunately, you can easily turn off the Emergency SOS feature on your iPhone 12 Mini. Overview of the iPhone 12 Mini The iPhone 12 Mini is the smallest of the four new iPhone 12 models.
